OL,3,CFaulty speed cameras: How to check if
OL,4,Cyou were fined by error
OL,6,FThousands of speeding fines could be
OL,7,Fcancelled after a "technical issue"
OL,8,Fsaw some speed cameras triggered
OL,9,Fincorrectly.
OL,11,FNational Highways has apologised for
OL,12,Fthe error, which meant a "very small
OL,13,Fnumber" of drivers had been fined
OL,14,Fincorrectly since 2021.
OL,16,FIt is understood that a software
OL,17,Fupdate created a problem with variable
OL,18,Fspeed cameras on some A roads and
OL,19,Fmotorways that led to drivers being
OL,20,Fincorrectly detected as speeding after
OL,21,Fthe speed limit had increased.
