OL,3,CFaulty speed cameras: How to check if
OL,4,Cyou were fined by error
OL,6,FAnyone who has been incorrectly fined
OL,7,Fwill be contacted directly by the
OL,8,Fpolice, with fines reimbursed and any
OL,9,Fpoints removed from their licence.
OL,11,FPolice forces have temporarily stopped
OL,12,Fissuing fines from variable cameras
OL,13,Funtil they have confidence nobody will
OL,14,Fbe wrongly prosecuted, but continue to
OL,15,Fenforce speed limits in other ways.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the National Police
OL,18,FChiefs' Council said police forces
OL,19,Fwere working to identify and contact
OL,20,F"a very limited number of motorists".
