OL,6,FThey added: "Policing enforces a range
OL,7,Fof offences, including speeding, on
OL,8,Fthe strategic road network through a
OL,9,Fnumber of tactics including mobile
OL,10,Fcamera deployments, roads policing
OL,11,Fpatrols and average speed sites. This
OL,12,Fremains unchanged.
OL,14,F"If you are affected by this issue,
OL,15,Fyou will be contacted and details of
OL,16,Fthe compensation scheme will be shared
OL,17,Fin due course. You do not need to take
OL,18,Fany action."
